- Displays GMB information
- Prioritizes local results

PLACEMENT:
Add to homepage:
<script type="application/ld+json">
[PASTE JSON HERE]
</script>

TESTING:
- Google Rich Results Test: https://search.google.com/test/rich-results
- Search your organization name (check Knowledge Panel)
- Verify all sameAs links work
- Confirm NAP consistency across web
*/
